title: Expelled Hero Is Too Strong
summary: Expelled Hero Is Too Strong Manhwa 파티에서 추방된 영웅이 너무 뛰어남 [독점] Synopsis : ” Yu jihan, you’re useless.” Yu jihan, a member of Kim hyuntae’s party, ‘Keroz’s’ rank 1 party, suddenly received a notice of expulsion. After 7 years of dedication, all he is left with is a severance pay of 10 million won. However that’s okay. I have ‘Sampling,’ the ability to see probability. [Chances of growing into a giant guild if you join the fun guild] [99%] I swear I’ll be more successful than you!
